I think the big thing about Copilot, everybody's used to the chat GPT interface, right?

00:01:18.239 --> 00:01:23.440
Of like where you're just like a chat back and forth with a superhuman artificial intelligence

00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:30.000
thing. Copilot is much more like recommendation driven, but you can actually talk to it.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:31.519
So I just did this a second ago.

00:01:31.519 --> 00:01:32.080
I'm curious.

00:01:33.199 --> 00:01:34.000
