I think that context is important, right?

00:03:03.039 --> 00:03:09.440
Like I think when I show people this for the first time, their like mental map is trying

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:16.320
to attach it to like the experience I've had interacting with chat GPT in a web browser.

00:03:16.320 --> 00:03:16.639
Right.

00:03:16.639 --> 00:03:23.600
And I think one of the big things that I think I would hone in on here is that we're a code

00:03:23.600 --> 00:03:25.440
force data science company, right?

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:29.440
Like we believe that the work that you're going to do is impacted with code.

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:31.759
It's you can take that build workflows.

00:03:31.759 --> 00:03:32.639
It's repeatable.

00:03:33.440 --> 00:03:37.199
So we have this pretty heavy prerequisite that you're going to be working with code,

00:03:37.199 --> 00:03:37.699
right?

00:03:38.639 --> 00:03:45.360
And to do that, like that happens in an environment where you're programming, right?

00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:47.839
