00:03:47.839 --> 00:03:50.800
Like this integrated development environment, which is our studio.

00:03:50.800 --> 00:03:56.639
So having a tool that's integrated into where the code first data science happens is a huge

00:03:56.639 --> 00:03:57.919
piece of the puzzle for me.

00:03:57.919 --> 00:04:02.399
And so that's why I like the fact that you're not running two screens.

00:04:02.399 --> 00:04:04.639
You've got chat GPT on one screen.

00:04:04.639 --> 00:04:07.600
